data.description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of Hartford, CT, 204-206 South St. presents a remarkable investment opportunity. This three-story property encompasses three distinct units, tailored for both comfort and convenience. With spacious layouts, two of these units feature three bedrooms and a bathroom each, while the third unit provides two bedrooms and a bathroom. Each unit in this property boasts hardwood flooring that extends throughout. The units have been thoughtfully updated, featuring newer walls, ceilings, and modern lighting fixtures. The heating system was recently completely upgraded including all new equipment, thermostats, etc. Outside, the property features a large yard and off-street parking is available. The design of the units emphasizes generous living and dining spaces, accompanied by comfortably sized bedrooms. Additionally, each unit also includes its own foyer. The property ensures financial ease for the owner, as it is separate gas for tenants, 1 furnace and 1 hot water heater. The recently entirely renovated available third-floor unit stands out as an ideal choice for owner-occupancy but also meets all necessary codes for housing and commanding a rent of $1950. This aligns with the proforma rents for the other floors, suggesting strong income potential across the property. Offering easy access to transportation and with Downtown Hartford just a stone's throw away, you don't want to miss out on this investment opportunity.
